steps.name: Click On Billed to Field and select FECO02 Billedto
click on Logistic Type and verify If there is any value for that field
Click on Logistic Type and select Outbond
Enter txt consignment : "UAT00211016"
Click On Second Stepper
Click and Select Sender Address
Select Sender Address from menu
Click On Step Receiver
Enter text Receiver Name
Select Receiver Name from dropdown list
Click On Stepper Step Value
Enter Text Step Value
Click on Stepper Requirment
Enter Text for Shipper Reference
Click on Standard Instruction type and select Future Delivery
Click on Standard Instruction type and select Future Date
Click on Standard INstruction Type and Select Do not deliver on date
Click On stepper Services
Verify the Rica is not present
Click On Service Type and select Next Day 17H00
Click On stepper Parcel
Enter text Number of parcel
Verify the parcel header is displayed
Click On Finalise Button and close the POPUP
click On PackageType01 and select Box1
verify the Security pack error is displayed
Click on Security Pack
verify the Security pack error is displayed
Enter text weight
Uncheck the print label check to generate the PDF Waybill
